<L>__{exterior sanchez's estate tree lined road day}
<A>__{a chalk white road, lined with trees. two liveried servants are walking down the road, one carrying a large silver tray, the other a smaller tray. they are overtaken by an administrator who hurries along the road, with documents under his arm.}
<L>__{exterior sanchez's estate stable block and paddock day}
<A>__{the clerk enters an imposing stable block. in the paddock, sanchez is training a magnificent young horse, making it step sideways, bending it to his will. the administrator watches him, unable to interrupt. behind him the two servants can be seen bringing in the silver trays, with covered dishes of food, a decanter of wine. they begin to lay them out on a table.}
